Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:54.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So she left the house to go shopping, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:07:00.98,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,High-grade steak, assorted sashimi, \Nand top-quality broiled eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.65,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,All portions for one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.30,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Now she's bought wine and two shortcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.90,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.30,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,She's smiling happily, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.69,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard carrying all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.87,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you carry it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.41,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.40,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're not suspicious children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.66,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,We're just considerate passers-by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.59,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.31,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clever strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:39.24,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The presence of children will \Ncreate a genial atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.27,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,increasing the chances Fujiki \NKazuma-san will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.30,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry the eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.55,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.82,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.95,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful not to break it.
