Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.69,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.59,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Think something of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.50,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, "Think nothing of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.14,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.23,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.25,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.60,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiki Kazuma will show up soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.11,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That call was from Fujiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:22.01,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He probably said he'd visit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:27.52,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yoda Satomi-san still has feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.82,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,If he was so desperate for cash \Nthat he robbed someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:35.61,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,then he must not be eating properly, \Nso she prepared a feast for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.46,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,She even withdrew a large amount of cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.87,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,She probably intends to give \Nit to him as getaway money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.19,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,But we just need to apprehend Fujiki Kazuma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.58,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,before she does anything \Nstupid like aid his getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:58.07,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but maybe Yoda Satomi-san \Nhas realized she's being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.21,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's too convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:06.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We nearly lost her while following her, \Nbut we found her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.27,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.07,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're overthinking it, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.10,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.66,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't Fujiki Kazuma show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.70,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three hours since \Nshe got the food and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.66,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.76,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.31,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoda Satomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:33.20,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.54,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Did Fujiki contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.28,DCItalic,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to \Ntell you. Could you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.05,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.08,DCItalic,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to discuss the details in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.47,DCItalic,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your little friends can come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.94,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,She invited all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.74,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:55.11,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, just after \Nyou left this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.86,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.35,DCFlashbackItalics,FUJIKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Haven't talked to you in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:10.23,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,He'd committed a crime and came to my \Napartment in hopes that I'd hide him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:14.00,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,but the police happened to be \Nthere, so he fled in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:18.46,DCFlashbackItalics,FUJIKI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get back together with you, \Nbut I guess things didn't go my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.99,DCFlashbackItalics,FUJIKI,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you find happiness, Satomi. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.26,DCFlashback,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:29.16,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,So Fujiki Kazuma came to \Nthis apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:34.50,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,But he saw us and fled \Nand called to say goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.65,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,which means he won't be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:41.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was that food and money for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.53,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. There was no need to get those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:49.04,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for tricking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:55.42,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized I was being watched, \NI decided to use that against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.00,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,By letting you observe me \Ngetting the food and money,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.55,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I made you believe Kazuma \Nwas trying to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:08.12,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I've realized allowing Kazuma to \Nstay on the run isn't good for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:12.02,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to tell you everything and ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:17.32,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,to please find Kazuma as soon as possible \Nand make him atone for his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:26.74,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We understand. In any case, we've \Nrealized it's pointless to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:30.71,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll call off our stakeout and \Nfollow Fujiki Kazuma's trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.21,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There's something off about Yoda Satomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She even cried tears \Nas she made that confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:48.42,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It smelled like an act to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.20,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Smelled like an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.02,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.57,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears may have been over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:04.15,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she still has \Nfeelings for Fujiki Kazuma-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.32,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,and they're deeply in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.22,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.02,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiki Kazuma-san came all \Nthe way to this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:24.75,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,saw the police, and fled in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.35,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll go farther and farther away \Nas they expand the area of their search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.31,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.99,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.88,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you discover a new fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:52.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Her confession was an act after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.25,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What happened as a result of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.29,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,The stakeout ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.59,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:05.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason Yoda Satomi-san was \Ninconvenienced by being watched by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.76,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.05,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:13.16,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiki Kazuma-san is \Nactually on his way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.60,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's no understanding women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.32,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't they cut ties with bad men?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.63,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.45,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a conversation grade \Nschool kids should be having.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.33,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's Detective Takagi's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.40,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Is your office in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.07,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:40.31,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're helping Detective Takagi with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.91,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.10,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.09,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.35,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,This is footage from this morning \Nof the front of this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.35,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,The people are small, so \NI'll enlarge the image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.23,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fujiki Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.18,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.96,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's really him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:05.92,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, based on the timestamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:10.20,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,we know he headed to Yoda \NSatomi-san's apartment this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.67,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,But the cameras only captured him arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.96,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever way he ran, \NI doubt he's still around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.84,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So, Inspector, we're \Ngoing to look for places
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.65,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiki Kazuma might go besides \NYoda Satomi-san's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.82,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.29,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:30.92,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.31,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.72,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Head directly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.30,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, should we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.48,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:50.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The police don't seem interested, \Nbut let's look into Yoda Satomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:59.77,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yoda Satomi-san used to be \Na really cheerful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:04.50,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,But around this time three years ago, \Nshe fell into a deep depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:08.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She probably took it hard when \NFujiki Kazuma-san dumped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.59,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I have some surprising news!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:15.13,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,She's currently seeing someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:22.77,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He runs a store on the other side \Nof the station, so I went to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.77,Default,SIGN TOP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fs23\shad0\pos(390,3)\c&HF2F8F4&\3c&H7264CD&}Ishinabe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.77,Default,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fs28\shad0\c&HF2F8F4&\3c&H7264CD&\frz20.84\pos(196,214)\frx2\fry356}Discount General Store
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.77,Default,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fs28\shad0\c&HF2F8F4&\3c&H7264CD&\pos(530,220)\frx4\fry6\frz334.3}Discount
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:27.63,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The owner is a good honest man \Nnamed Ishinabe-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:28.15,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)\pos(322,296)\3c&HAD746B&}Ishinabe Daisuke (30)\NStore Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:32.63,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but the shocking part is he got engaged \Nto Yoda Satomi-san last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.91,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:41.48,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,An engaged woman wouldn't trick the police \Nto help a man she got over a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.33,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That confession must have been a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.43,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she need to lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.80,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The only trail the police have on Fujiki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:56.18,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,is him heading to Yoda \NSatomi-san's apartment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.57,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was captured on a security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.90,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:05.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Being watched is inconvenient both \Nwhen you're secretly receiving a guest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.84,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and when they're leaving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.53,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea books could be so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.41,DCMain,ISHINABE,0000,0000,0000,,You should've had them pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:21.29,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Used bookstores pick up? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.04,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.42,DCMain,ISHINABE,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got work, so \NI'm heading back to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.72,DCMain,ISHINABE,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.05,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.68,DCMain,ISHINABE,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.63,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:46.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoda Satomi-san. Could you show us \Nthat box you loaded into your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.98,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,They're just books I finished reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:52.79,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. Don't lock the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.83,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:55.86,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.38,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:00.97,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But they're just books, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:17.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiki Kazuma-san, who injured \Nsomeone in a robbery this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,fled to your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't want to be arrested, \Nso he asked you to hide him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:29.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But you couldn't forgive him for selfishly \Nbegging for help after dumping you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.15,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,so you killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:40.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,When you returned to your senses, you \Nrealized the gravity of what you'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:45.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If your crime was discovered, your \Nengagement would be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So you decided to abandon Fujiki-san's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:54.15,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it were discovered, your \Nrelationship ended three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.59,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You figured the police wouldn't suspect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.97,DCFlashback,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.26,DCFlashbackItalics,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but we're with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.73,DCFlashback,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,B-Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:20.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Then they began their stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.90,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You were aghast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:28.16,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The police were watching you at all times, \Nso you couldn't move the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.23,DCFlashback,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:38.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's when you came up \Nwith the fake confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.98,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You had two goals in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:46.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,First, to make them call off their stakeout, \Nand second, to avoid suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You were willing to deceive \Nthe police to help him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It would convince the police
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:59.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,that someone who loved Fujiki-san that much \Nwouldn't kill him or dump his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:04.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You probably meant to leave \NFujiki-san's body somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:08.71,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and lead them to believe he got involved \Nin some kind of trouble while on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:15.38,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're mostly correct, but you \Ngot one important thing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.34,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't kill Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.34,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,When he came to my place, \NKazuma said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.09,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't seriously serve water \Nto a man you haven't seen in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.01,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.90,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,You're as inconsiderate as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.91,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,Treat your guests better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.15,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.28,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,I finally realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.66,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,You were my bluebird of happiness all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:55.41,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad you waited three years, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:02.93,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking I once loved \Nthis man made me feel pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.84,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd grown over those three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:07.57,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.94,DCFlashback,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not some innocent girl anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:11.81,DCFlashback,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.31,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.95,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:25.20,DCFlashback,KAZUMA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:48.88,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,If a neighbor heard us shouting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:53.10,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,the police would suspect \NI killed him during an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.86,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,So I felt I had to do \Nsomething about Kazuma's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:02.33,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,If that's truly what happened, we'll \Ntreat this as an accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.53,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for calling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:09.24,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this man involved in the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.54,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ishinabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.87,DCMain,ISHINABE,0000,0000,0000,,I came back because I forgot my lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.03,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.93,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,A man died, and I didn't call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.22,DCMain,SATOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Instead I hid the body and \Nplanned to get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.61,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest for \Nattempting to abandon a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.40,DCMain,ISHINABE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:09.32,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man. I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:12.41,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, all we had to eat \Nwere those snacks during the stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:16.68,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wasn't she arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.79,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to \Nthe top-quality eel she bought?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.54,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,And the shortcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:28.67,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But she was arrested, so \Nwouldn't those be evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:33.59,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they were probably collected \Nas evidence of her deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:36.93,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man. My eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.44,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.44,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:40.64,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have the professor treat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.20,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:44.57,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1440)}Good thinking, Haibara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:24:09.09,DCEpPreview,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:47.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Miyano Akemi-san was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:52.55,DCMain,MURATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're her younger sister Shiho-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:54.49,DCItalic,WAKASA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.21,0:23:56.99,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a smart kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:24:00.33,DCMain,YANAGIMACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm with the Beika Fire Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:02.62,DCMain,MURATA,0000,0000,0000,,She was the better...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:06.74,DCMain,KOBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:15.09,DCNextEp,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Miyano Akemi's Time Capsule (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:14.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "Miyano \NAkemi's Time Capsule, Part One!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.11,0:24:32.65,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
